description:
The Battle of Mexico City is the second video release by Rage Against the Machine. The concert was recorded in Mexico City&amp;#039;s MX Palacio de Deportes in 1999 as part of their Battle of Los Angeles world tour. The city was chosen as the band had been longtime supporters of various political causes in Mexico (it was also the first time they had played there).

